attributionInfo.brokerName: RE/MAX at Barnegat Bay - Forked River
RE/MAX at Barnegat Bay - Forked River

data.description: Welcome to the Jersey Shore! With stunning, unobstructed views of Barnegat Bay, this charming, fully updated bungalow sits across from Forked River Beach Bayfront Park. This home features an open floor plan, freshly painted cathedral ceilings with a newer kitchen complete with center island and SS appliances. The list of updates is extensive; roof with transferable warranty, siding and gutters, heating and central air, hot water heater, newer floors throughout and updated windows and doors. Backyard is completely fenced in with a paver patio and above ground pool (2 yrs young)
